Ashtukzu II was the third King of the Mulan Dynasty who ruled the city-state of Westgate.
Ashtukzu II was the son and rightful heir of the throne, but his cousin Thunn ousted his father, King Ashtukzu I, and claimed the throne for himself. Ashtukzu II avenged his father in the , when he overthrew his cousin and became king. He reigned until the .
